  <refnamediv>
    <refname>biggrep.conf</refname>
    <refpurpose>Configuration file for bgsearch default options.</refpurpose>
  </refnamediv>
  <refsect1>
    <title>Description</title>
    <para>
    <filename>/etc/biggrep/biggrep.conf</filename> contains settings
    that override defaults for bgsearch.  All long-form options for
    bgssearch (see <citerefentry><refentrytitle>bgseaarch</refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry>)are supported.  This
    man page describes the most useful options for inclusion in this
    file.</para>
  </refsect1>
  <refsect1>
    <title>File Format</title>
    <para>The general format of this file consists of key=value
    pairs. Only one key=value pair may be present on a line, and
    the value must be separated from the key by a '=' character.
    For keys that require no value, listing the key alone (without
    a '=' character) will set that value to true. All long-form
    options for bgssearch (see <citerefentry><refentrytitle>bgseaarch</refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry>)are
    supported. Lines beginning with the '#' character are ignored.</para>
    <variablelist>
      <varlistentry>
        <term><option>directory</option>=<replaceable><filename class="directory">DIR</filename></replaceable></term>
        <listitem>
          <para>
            <xi:include href="bgsearch.1.xml" xpointer="xpointer(//*[@id='directorydesc']/node())"/>
          </para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>
      <varlistentry>
        <term><option>recursive</option></term>
        <listitem>
          <para>
            <xi:include href="bgsearch.1.xml" xpointer="xpointer(//*[@id='recursivedesc']/node())"/>
          </para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>
      <varlistentry>
        <term><option>no-metadata</option></term>
        <listitem>
          <para>
            <xi:include href="bgsearch.1.xml" xpointer="xpointer(//*[@id='nometadesc']/node())"/>
          </para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>
      <varlistentry>
        <term><option>verify</option></term>
        <listitem>
          <para>
            <xi:include href="bgsearch.1.xml" xpointer="xpointer(//*[@id='verifydesc']/node())"/>
          </para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>
      <varlistentry>
        <term><option>limit</option>=<replaceable>NUM</replaceable></term>
        <listitem>
          <para>
            <xi:include href="bgsearch.1.xml" xpointer="xpointer(//*[@id='limitdesc']/node())"/>
          </para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>
      <varlistentry>
        <term><option>numprocs</option>=<replaceable>NUM</replaceable></term>
        <listitem>
          <para>
            <xi:include href="bgsearch.1.xml" xpointer="xpointer(//*[@id='numprocsdesc']/node())"/>
          </para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>
      <varlistentry>
        <term><option>banner</option>=<replaceable><filename class="directory">PATH</filename></replaceable></term>
        <listitem>
          <para>
            <xi:include href="bgsearch.1.xml" xpointer="xpointer(//*[@id='bannerdesc']/node())"/>
          </para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>
    </variablelist>
  </refsect1>
  <refsect1 id='biggrepexamples'>
    <title>EXAMPLES</title>
    <example>
      <title>Example biggrep configuration file:</title>
      <programlisting>
directory=/data/biggrep/indexes
banner=/etc/biggrep/usage-warning.txt
</programlisting>
    </example>
  </refsect1>
